### Q2: Tool Selection — LLM tool seçərkən necə qərar verir?

**Cavab:** LLM **heç vaxt tool seçmir**. Tool seçimi 100% deterministikdir — [ToolScheduler](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#181-450) pre-condition əsasında qərar verir.

#### ToolScheduler Dependency Graph ([tool_scheduler.py#L71-L128](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#L71-L128)):

```python
TOOL_DEPENDENCY_GRAPH = {
    "nmap_scan": {
        "pre": [],                                    # ← Heç bir pre-condition yoxdur
        "post": ["open_ports", "services", "os_detection"],
        "cmd": "nmap -sV -sC -O {target}",
        "binary": "nmap",
    },
    "nuclei_scan": {
        "pre": ["open_ports"],                        # ← nmap tamamlansa çalışır
        "post": ["cve_matches", "nuclei_results"],
    },
    "gobuster_scan": {
        "pre": ["http_confirmed"],                    # ← HTTP servisi varsa çalışır
        "post": ["directories", "hidden_paths"],
    },
    "sqlmap_scan": {
        "pre": ["http_confirmed", "directories"],     # ← gobuster + http lazımdır
    },
}
```

#### Pre-condition Check ([tool_scheduler.py#L233-L250](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#L233-L250)):

```python
def get_ready_tools(self) -> List[str]:
    ready = []
    for tool_name, spec in self.tdg.items():
        if tool_name in self.results:      continue  # artıq icra edilib
        if tool_name in self._unavailable: continue  # binary yoxdur
        pre = spec.get("pre", [])
        if all(self.kg.has_capability(p) for p in pre):  # BÜTÜN pre-conditionlar KG-dədir
            ready.append(tool_name)
    return ready
```

> **Nəticə:** Function calling JSON schema **istifadə olunmur**. [ToolScheduler](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#181-450) LLM-dən tamamilə müstəqildir — tool-ları KG capability flag-larına əsasən deterministik icra edir.

