### Q3: Hypothesis → Exploit Path

**Cavab:** [HypothesisEngine](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/hypothesis_engine.py#149-364) hypothesis yaradır → [ParallelExploitOrchestrator](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/parallel_exploit.py#129-321) onları prioritized queue-ya qoyur → hər hypothesis [_test_single_hypothesis()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/exploit_phase_agent.py#171-184)-ə göndərilir.

#### Tam axın:

```
[exploit_phase_agent.py#L117-L167]

async def execute(self):
    # ── 1. KG-dən context yüklə ──
    context = self._load_context_from_kg()

    # ── 2. Hypothesis yarat ──
    hypotheses = self.hypothesis_engine.generate(self.target)

    # ── 3. Parallel icra et ──
    orchestrator = ParallelExploitOrchestrator(max_concurrent=4)
    parallel_result = await orchestrator.run_all(
        hypotheses=hypotheses,
        test_fn=self._test_single_hypothesis,    # ← hər hypothesis bura gedir
        record_fn=self._record_result,
    )
```

#### HypothesisEngine → Hypothesis yaratma ([hypothesis_engine.py#L130-L200](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/hypothesis_engine.py#L130-L200)):

```python
def generate(self, target: str) -> List[Hypothesis]:
    vulnerabilities = self.kg.get_vulnerabilities_for_host(target)
    services = self.kg.get_services_for_host(target)

    # Layer 1: CVE-based (yüksək confidence)
    for vuln in vulnerabilities.get("vulnerabilities", []):
        hypotheses.append(Hypothesis(
            cve=vuln["cve"],
            target_service=service_name,
            confidence=0.80,       # ← CVE varsa yüksək
        ))

    # Layer 2: Service-based (aşağı confidence)
    for svc in services.get("services", []):
        # Port-a görə default exploit vector seçir
        hypotheses.append(Hypothesis(
            attack_vector="default_creds",
            confidence=0.50,
        ))

    # Layer 3: Memory adjustment
    recall = self.memory.recall(self.target)
    for h in hypotheses:
        adj = recall.get_confidence_adjustment(h.cve, h.target_service, h.version)
        h.confidence += adj        # ← Keçmiş sessiya uğursuzsa confidence azalır
```

> **Nəticə:** Hypothesis → ExploitLoop yolu: [generate()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/reporting/causal_chain.py#56-81) → [PriorityHypothesisQueue](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/parallel_exploit.py#64-110) (max-heap, ən yüksək confidence birinci) → [_test_single_hypothesis()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/exploit_phase_agent.py#171-184) → direct test və ya LLM sandbox.

