## 📋 SECTION 2: TOOL EXECUTION

### Q4: ToolScheduler — [get_ready_tools()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#233-251) nəticəsi necə istifadə olunur?

**Cavab:** [get_ready_tools()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#233-251) nəticəsi **LLM-ə verilmir**. Birbaşa `ToolScheduler.run()` daxilində istifadə olunur.

#### Execution Loop ([tool_scheduler.py#L362-L415](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#L362-L415)):

```python
async def run(self) -> Dict[str, ToolResult]:
    while iteration < max_iterations:
        # 1. Mümkün olmayan tool-ları skip et
        for tool in self.get_skippable_tools():
            self.results[tool] = ToolResult(status=ToolStatus.SKIPPED)

        # 2. Hazır tool-ları tap
        ready = self.get_ready_tools()
        if not ready:
            break

        # 3. Parallel icra et (max 3)
        batch = ready[:self.max_parallel]
        tasks = [self.execute_tool(tool) for tool in batch]
        await asyncio.gather(*tasks, return_exceptions=True)

        # 4. Yeni capabilities → yeni tool-lar unlock olur → loop davam edir
```

#### Tool Execution ([tool_scheduler.py#L290-L360](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_scheduler.py#L290-L360)):

```python
async def execute_tool(self, tool_name: str) -> ToolResult:
    cmd = spec["cmd"].format(target=self.target, http_port=http_port)
    proc = await asyncio.create_subprocess_shell(cmd, ...)
    stdout, stderr = await asyncio.wait_for(proc.communicate(), timeout=...)

    # Post-conditions KG-yə yazılır
    for cap in spec.get("post", []):
        self.kg.set_capability(cap)
```

> **Nəticə:** ToolScheduler tamamilə **deterministik** və **LLM-siz** çalışır. Pre-condition → KG check → binary check → subprocess icra → post-condition write.

