### Q5: Parallel Execution — Port Lock Mexanizmi

**Cavab:** [PortLockManager](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/parallel_exploit.py#35-59) hər port üçün ayrı `asyncio.Lock` saxlayır. Eyni porta yönəlmiş iki hypothesis eyni anda çalışa bilmir.

#### Mexanizm ([parallel_exploit.py#L35-L58](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/parallel_exploit.py#L35-L58)):

```python
class PortLockManager:
    def __init__(self):
        self._locks: Dict[int, asyncio.Lock] = {}

    def get_lock(self, port: int) -> asyncio.Lock:
        if port not in self._locks:
            self._locks[port] = asyncio.Lock()   # ← Port başına bir lock
        return self._locks[port]
```

#### İstifadə ([parallel_exploit.py#L256-L265](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/parallel_exploit.py#L256-L265)):

```python
async def _run_single(self, hypothesis, ...):
    async with self.semaphore:              # ← Max 4 concurrent
        port_lock = self.port_locks.get_lock(hypothesis.port)
        async with port_lock:               # ← Port 80-ə yönəlmiş 2 hypothesis sıra ilə
            evidence = await test_fn(hypothesis)
```

#### Early Termination ([parallel_exploit.py#L289-L297](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/parallel_exploit.py#L289-L297)):

```python
if evidence.success and evidence.access_gained:
    result.successes.append(evidence)
    if not self.success_event.is_set():
        self.first_success_id = hypothesis.id
        self.success_event.set()  # ← asyncio.Event() ilə digər task-lara signal
