### Q6: ReconPhaseAgent — LLM-siz Necə Çalışır?

**Cavab:** [ReconPhaseAgent](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/recon_phase_agent.py#63-386) **100% tool-driven**-dir, heç bir LLM call yoxdur.

#### İki Strategiya ([recon_phase_agent.py#L86-L117](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/recon_phase_agent.py#L86-L117)):

```python
async def execute(self) -> dict:
    # Strategy 1: nmap (subprocess)
    result = await self._nmap_scan()    # nmap -sV -sC -T4 --open -oX -
    if result and result.get("open_ports"):
        result["scan_type"] = "nmap"
        return result

    # Strategy 2: Python socket scan (nmap yoxdursa)
    result = await self._python_scan()  # asyncio.open_connection() ilə
    result["scan_type"] = "python_fallback"
    return result
```

#### Python Fallback Scanner ([recon_phase_agent.py#L260-L282](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/recon_phase_agent.py#L260-L282)):

```python
async def _async_port_scan(self) -> List[int]:
    async def check_port(port: int):
        conn = asyncio.open_connection(self.target, port)
        reader, writer = await asyncio.wait_for(conn, timeout=1.5)
        return port  # Açıqdırsa port nömrəsini qaytar

    tasks = [check_port(p) for p in COMMON_PORTS]  # 27 port
    results = await asyncio.gather(*tasks, return_exceptions=True)
```

#### KG-yə Yazma ([recon_phase_agent.py#L351-L386](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/recon_phase_agent.py#L351-L386)):

```python
def _write_to_kg(self, result: dict):
    self.kg.add_host(self.target)
    for svc in result.get("services", []):
        self.kg.add_port(self.target, svc["port"], "open")
        self.kg.add_service(self.target, svc["port"], svc["name"], svc["version"])

    # Capability flags for ToolScheduler
    if name in ("http", "https"):
        self.kg.set_capability("http_confirmed", True)
    if name == "ssh":
        self.kg.set_capability("ssh_confirmed", True)
```

