### Q7: KG Data Model — Node və Edge Strukturu

**Cavab:** KG NetworkX `DiGraph` istifadə edir. 8 node tipi, 8 edge tipi var.

#### Node Types ([knowledge_graph.py#L29-L38](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/knowledge_graph.py#L29-L38)):

| Node Type | ID Format | Attributes |
|-----------|-----------|------------|
| HOST | `"10.10.10.5"` | os, hostname |
| PORT | `"10.10.10.5:80"` | port, state |
| SERVICE | `"10.10.10.5:80:nginx"` | name, version |
| VULNERABILITY | `"vuln:CVE-2021-41773"` | cve, severity, cvss |
| EXPLOIT | `"exploit:CVE-2021-41773:path_traversal"` | name, url, tested |
| CREDENTIAL | `"cred:10.10.10.5:admin"` | username, password, source |
| FILE | `"file:10.10.10.5:/etc/shadow"` | path, content_preview |
| VERSION | — | — |

#### Edge Types ([knowledge_graph.py#L41-L51](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/knowledge_graph.py#L41-L51)):

```
HOST ──HAS_PORT──→ PORT ──RUNS_SERVICE──→ SERVICE ──HAS_VULN──→ VULNERABILITY ──EXPLOITABLE_VIA──→ EXPLOIT
HOST ──USES_CREDENTIAL──→ CREDENTIAL
HOST ──CONTAINS_FILE──→ FILE
HOST ──CONNECTS_TO──→ HOST (lateral movement)
```

#### Capability System ([knowledge_graph.py#L81-L92](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/knowledge_graph.py#L81-L92)):

```python
# KG-nin ayrı _capabilities dict-i var (graph-dan ayrı)
self._capabilities: Dict[str, Any] = {}

def set_capability(self, name: str, value: Any = True):
    self._capabilities[name] = value  # "http_confirmed": True

def has_capability(self, name: str) -> bool:
    return bool(self._capabilities.get(name))
```

> **Nəticə:** KG iki təbəqədən ibarətdir: **NetworkX graph** (strukturlu məlumat) + **_capabilities dict** (ToolScheduler üçün flag-lar).

