### Q9: ShellBridge — Transport Seçimi

**Cavab:** `ShellBridge.from_kg()` KG-dəki exploit node-larını oxuyur və attack_vector-a görə transport seçir.

#### Attack Vector → Shell Type Mapping ([shell_bridge.py#L62-L83](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/shell_bridge.py#L62-L83)):

```python
METHOD_TO_SHELL = {
    "ftp_anonymous":     ShellType.FTP,       → FTPTransport (ftplib)
    "default_creds":     ShellType.SSH,        → SSHTransport (asyncssh/paramiko)
    "postgres_noauth":   ShellType.DB_POSTGRES,→ PostgresTransport (asyncpg/psycopg2)
    "web_shell_upload":  ShellType.WEB,        → WebShellTransport (http.client)
    "rce":               ShellType.WEB,        → WebShellTransport
}
```

#### Factory Method ([shell_bridge.py#L519-L561](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/shell_bridge.py#L519-L561)):

```python
@classmethod
def from_kg(cls, kg, target) -> Optional["ShellBridge"]:
    exploit_info = cls._get_exploit_info_from_kg(kg, target)
    best = cls._select_best_exploit(exploit_info)  # success > tested > first

    method = best.get("attack_vector")
    shell_type = METHOD_TO_SHELL.get(method, ShellType.BASH_LOCAL)

    # KG-dən credential al
    creds = cls._get_credentials_from_kg(kg, target)

    transport_class = cls.TRANSPORT_MAP[shell_type]
    return cls(transport=transport_class(ctx), context=ctx)
```

#### PostgreSQL Shell-to-SQL Translation ([shell_bridge.py#L365-L377](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/shell_bridge.py#L365-L377)):

```python
def _shell_to_sql(self, command: str) -> str:
    if cmd.startswith("cat "):
        return f"SELECT pg_read_file('{filepath}', 0, 10000)"
    elif cmd in ("whoami", "id"):
        return "SELECT current_user, session_user"
    elif cmd == "uname -a":
        return "SELECT version()"
    return cmd  # SQL olaraq göndər
```

