).fetchall()
```

#### Layer 2: Semantic (Fingerprint Match) ([persistent_memory.py#L356-L370](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/persistent_memory.py#L356-L370)):

```python
# Fərqli target-lərdə eyni service+version combo
fingerprint = compute_fingerprint(services)  # sha256 hash
similar_rows = self.conn.execute(
    "SELECT ... FROM attempts WHERE fingerprint = ? AND target != ?",
    (fingerprint, target),
).fetchall()
```

#### Confidence Adjustment ([persistent_memory.py#L97-L122](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/persistent_memory.py#L97-L122)):

```python
def get_confidence_adjustment(self, cve, service, version):
    # Exact match: -0.15 * attempt_count (uğursuzluq), +0.20 (uğur)
    # Similar match: -0.08 (uğursuzluq), +0.15 (uğur)
    return max(-0.8, min(0.5, adjustment))  # Clamp
```

#### HypothesisEngine-də istifadəsi ([hypothesis_engine.py#L266-L275](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/hypothesis_engine.py#L266-L275)):

```python
# Memory recall
recall = self.memory.recall(self.target)
for h in hypotheses:
    adj = recall.get_confidence_adjustment(h.cve, h.target_service, h.version)
    h.confidence = max(0.05, min(0.99, h.confidence + adj))
```

> **Nəticə:** Əgər CVE-2021-41773 3 dəfə uğursuz olubsa: `confidence -= 0.15 * 3 = -0.45`. Növbəti sessiyada bu hypothesis sonuncu sıraya düşür.

