#### WAF → Mutation Sırası ([adaptive_mutation.py#L279-L306](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py#L279-L306)):

```python
MUTATION_STRATEGIES = {
    ResponseClass.WAF_DETECTED: [
        MutationStrategy.CASE_VARIATION,         # SeLeCt
        MutationStrategy.COMMENT_INJECTION,      # SE/**/LECT
        MutationStrategy.DOUBLE_URL_ENCODE,      # %2527
        MutationStrategy.UNICODE_NORMALIZATION,   # ＇ (fullwidth)
        MutationStrategy.HPP,                    # param=safe&param=malicious
        MutationStrategy.CHUNKED_TRANSFER,
        MutationStrategy.NULL_BYTE,              # %00
        MutationStrategy.NEWLINE_INJECTION,      # CRLF
    ],
    ResponseClass.RATE_LIMITED: [
        MutationStrategy.DELAY_RETRY,            # Gözlə və təkrarla
    ],
}
```

