#### Mövcud Qoruma ([exploit_phase_agent.py#L580-L600](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/exploit_phase_agent.py#L580-L600)):

