### Q20: Adaptive Mutation → Exploit Pipeline İnteqrasiyası

**Cavab:** [AdaptivePayloadMutator](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py#318-504) tam implement olunub, amma **exploit pipeline ilə inteqrasiya olunmayıb**.

#### Mövcud Sistem (İnteqrasiya olunmamış):

```
ExploitPhaseAgent._test_single_hypothesis()
    └→ direct socket test (FTP/SSH/HTTP)
    └→ _sandbox_llm_test()  ← LLM kod yazır, bir dəfə icra edir
                              ↑ ExploitLoop ÇAĞIRILMIR
```

#### Nəzərdə tutulan Sistem (İnteqrasiya edilsə):

```
ExploitPhaseAgent._test_single_hypothesis()
    └→ direct socket test
    └→ ExploitLoop.run(               ← BU İSTİFADƏ OLUNMUR
           hypothesis_id,
           initial_payload,
           tool_fn=self._execute_payload,
           max_iterations=10
       )
       └→ Classify response
       └→ WAF? → Mutation → Retry
       └→ Vulnerable? → SUCCESS
```

> [!CAUTION]
> **Böyük Boşluq:** [adaptive_mutation.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py) **768 sətir** tam işləyən koddur — [ResponseClassifier](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py#121-250), [AdaptivePayloadMutator](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py#318-504), [ExploitLoop](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py#545-768) hamısı implement olunub. Lakin [exploit_phase_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/exploit_phase_agent.py)-da **[ExploitLoop](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/adaptive_mutation.py#545-768) heç yerdə import və ya istifadə olunmur**. Bu o deməkdir ki, WAF aşkarlandıqda heç bir bypass cəhdi olmur — hypothesis sadəcə "failed" olaraq qeyd olunur.

